    "missionDesc": "Tibyaan Academy was founded with a simple mission: to make quality Quran and Islamic education accessible to every Muslim, anywhere in the world. We combine the authenticity of traditional Islamic scholarship with the convenience of modern technology, offering live 1-on-1 classes with certified teachers, AI-powered learning tools, and a comprehensive curriculum from Nazra to Aalim course.",
